{"name":"Cook's Mate Tasks","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_7xbqzd9z21","path":"Seas of Eberron","color":"#008000"}},"img":"modules/savage-eberron-artwork/assets/icons/logo-eberron-circle-white.webp","description":"","results":[{"_id":"rhr7QnK5vRLUwwQ3","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<div class=\"swade-core\"><strong>Cooking:</strong> Assisting Ambrose Kroop in preparing the day’s meal. If Kroop is sober, no check is required. If Kroop is drunk, this requires a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Survival]{Survival} check.</div>","img":"modules/savage-eberron-artwork/assets/icons/logo-eberron-circle-black.webp","resultId":"","weight":2,"range":[1,2],"drawn":false},{"_id":"SAgNGcewddxWrQzc","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<div class=\"swade-core\"><strong>Fishing:</strong> Catching tonight’s supper using the ship’s nets. A @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Survival]{Survival} check provides enough fish. A failed check results in a day in the bilges as punishment the following day.</div>","img":"modules/savage-eberron-artwork/assets/icons/logo-eberron-circle-black.webp","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false},{"_id":"CoHH8lFZNgTdz1LN","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<div class=\"swade-core\"><strong>Turtle Hunting:</strong> Hunting leatherback sea turtles with harpoons, treble hooks, and nets. A @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Survival]{Survival} check provides enough food. A failed check results in a day in the bilges as punishment the following day.</div>","img":"modules/savage-eberron-artwork/assets/icons/logo-eberron-circle-black.webp","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false},{"_id":"DdbDaQtWyqS5xHSV","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<div class=\"swade-core\"><strong>Bull Session:</strong> Drinking with Ambrose Kroop and listening to his stories. The cook’s mate must drink an additional rum ration, but is able to take an additional ship action during the day.</div>","img":"modules/savage-eberron-artwork/assets/icons/logo-eberron-circle-black.webp","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false},{"_id":"obMkrIakhYK1Rswt","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<div class=\"swade-core\"><strong>Special Occasion:</strong> Captain Harrigan is celebrating something today, and wants one of the ship’s pigs butchered and cooked for dinner. The PC must make a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Survival]{Survival} check to slaughter the animal, then help Kroop to clean, cut, and prepare the carcass. If Kroop is sober, no additional check is required. If Kroop is drunk, this requires a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Survival]{Survival} check.</div>","img":"modules/savage-eberron-artwork/assets/icons/logo-eberron-circle-black.webp","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false}],"formula":"1d6","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"_id":"mQzMFly3Jnn0DFIA"}
{"name":"Rigging Tasks","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_7xbqzd9z21","path":"Seas of Eberron","color":"#008000"}},"img":"modules/savage-eberron-artwork/assets/icons/logo-eberron-circle-white.webp","description":"","results":[{"_id":"rhr7QnK5vRLUwwQ3","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<div class=\"swade-core\"><strong>Rigging Repair:</strong> The ship’s rigging frequently gets damaged and must be repaired, requiring an @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Athletics]{Athletics} check to reach the rigging 30 feet up, followed by a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Boating]{Boating} or @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Athletics]{Athletics} check.</div>","img":"modules/savage-eberron-artwork/assets/icons/logo-eberron-circle-black.webp","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false},{"_id":"20KkIn7MQiImtibx","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<div class=\"swade-core\"><strong>Line Work:</strong> Hard work hoisting and lowering sails, requiring a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Boating]{Boating} or @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Athletics]{Athletics} check. The character must also make a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Vigor} check to avoid being @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Fatigue]{Fatigued} at the end of the shift.</div>","img":"modules/savage-eberron-artwork/assets/icons/logo-eberron-circle-black.webp","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false},{"_id":"SAgNGcewddxWrQzc","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<div class=\"swade-core\"><strong>Upper Rigging Work:</strong> Work in the upper rigging, 50 feet up, requiring an @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Athletics]{Athletics} check, followed by a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Boating]{Boating} or @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Athletics]{Athletics} check.</div>","img":"modules/savage-eberron-artwork/assets/icons/logo-eberron-circle-black.webp","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false},{"_id":"CoHH8lFZNgTdz1LN","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<div class=\"swade-core\"><strong>Rope Work:</strong> Handling the ship’s ropes, including coiling them, stowing them, and securing them to cleats and single and double bollards, requiring a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Boating]{Boating} or @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Athletics]{Athletics} check.</div>","img":"modules/savage-eberron-artwork/assets/icons/logo-eberron-circle-black.webp","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false},{"_id":"DdbDaQtWyqS5xHSV","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<div class=\"swade-core\"><strong>Lookout:</strong> A climb to the crow’s nest 60 feet up, requiring @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Athletics]{Athletics} check followed by a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Notice]{Notice} check.</div>","img":"modules/savage-eberron-artwork/assets/icons/logo-eberron-circle-black.webp","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false},{"_id":"obMkrIakhYK1Rswt","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<div class=\"swade-core\"><strong>Mainsail Duties:</strong> Tough work raising and lowering the mainsail, requiring a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Boating]{Boating} or @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Athletics]{Athletics} check. The character must also make a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Vigor} check to avoid being @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Fatigue]{Fatigued} at the end of the shift.</div>","img":"modules/savage-eberron-artwork/assets/icons/logo-eberron-circle-black.webp","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false}],"formula":"1d6","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"_id":"0xBh1BQQGZv23FgI"}
{"name":"Swab Tasks","permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"flags":{"journal-links":{},"cf":{"id":"temp_7xbqzd9z21","path":"Seas of Eberron","color":"#008000"}},"img":"modules/savage-eberron-artwork/assets/icons/logo-eberron-circle-white.webp","description":"","results":[{"_id":"rhr7QnK5vRLUwwQ3","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<div class=\"swade-core\"><strong>Man the Bilges:</strong> Vile and sweaty work cleaning out the bilges, requiring an @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Athletics]{Athletics} (–1) check. The character must also make a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Vigor} check to avoid being @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Fatigue]{Fatigued} at the end of the shift.</div>","img":"modules/savage-eberron-artwork/assets/icons/logo-eberron-circle-black.webp","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false},{"_id":"20KkIn7MQiImtibx","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<div class=\"swade-core\"><strong>Rat Catcher:</strong> Catching rats and other vermin belowdecks, requiring either a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Stealth]{Stealth} check or @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Survival]{Survival} check to catch and kill enough rats, cockroaches, and beetles for a good day’s work.</div>","img":"modules/savage-eberron-artwork/assets/icons/logo-eberron-circle-black.webp","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false},{"_id":"SAgNGcewddxWrQzc","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<div class=\"swade-core\"><strong>Swab the Decks:</strong> Backbreaking work mopping the decks and scrubbing them with sandstone blocks called holystones, requiring an @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Athletics]{Athletics} or @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Vigor} check. Failing either check results in the character being @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Fatigue]{Fatigued} at the end of the shift.</div>","img":"modules/savage-eberron-artwork/assets/icons/logo-eberron-circle-black.webp","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false},{"_id":"CoHH8lFZNgTdz1LN","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<div class=\"swade-core\"><strong>Hauling Rope and Knot Work:</strong> Tying and untying knots in the ship’s ropes and moving heavy coils of rope from one part of the ship to another, requiring a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Boating]{Boating} or @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Athletics]{Athletics} check. The character must also make a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Vigor} check to avoid being @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Fatigue]{Fatigued} at the end of the shift.</div>","img":"modules/savage-eberron-artwork/assets/icons/logo-eberron-circle-black.webp","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false},{"_id":"DdbDaQtWyqS5xHSV","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<div class=\"swade-core\"><strong>Runner:</strong> Passing messages to the crew and officers of the <em>Wormwood</em> in all parts of the ship except officers’ cabins, requiring an @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Athletics]{Athletics} check and @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Vigor} check. Failing the @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Traits]{Vigor} check results in the character being @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Fatigue]{Fatigued} at the end of the shift.</div>","img":"modules/savage-eberron-artwork/assets/icons/logo-eberron-circle-black.webp","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false},{"_id":"obMkrIakhYK1Rswt","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<div class=\"swade-core\"><strong>Repairs:</strong> Things constantly tear or break aboard the ship and need repairs, whether sewing sails or splicing rope all day, requiring a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-skills.Boating]{Boating} or @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Athletics]{Athletics} check.</div>","img":"modules/savage-eberron-artwork/assets/icons/logo-eberron-circle-black.webp","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false}],"formula":"1d6","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"_id":"Sk981H2ife8Cy1UG"}
